articles.title: Can diabetic patients eat jackfruit or mangoes? Here's what health expert says - Asianet Newsable
articles.description: Can diabetics consume mango and jackfruit? Dr. Lalitha Appukuttan, a specialist in weight loss and the head of the naturopathy department at NIMS Medicity in Thiruvananthapuram, has this to say.
